---
title: Roasted Cauliflower Steaks with Bulgur, Tzatziki, and Spiced Oil
description: Roasting cauliflower in thick slices transforms it into a hearty main dish! Tzatziki - everyone's favorite Greek condiment - is a tangy, protein-packed topping for these steaks. Serves on a bed of whole grain bulgur, it’s both healthy and filling.
